          "name": "main.py",
          "language": "py",
          "contents": "def turn_off_lights():\n  # Prints a message to turn off the lights\n  print(\"Don't forget to turn off the lights when you leave a room.\")\n\ndef use_reusable_bottle():\n  # Prints a reminder message to bring a reusable water bottle\n  print(\"Bring a reusable water bottle instead of buying plastic ones.\")\n\n# TODO - Write the daily_reminder() function\n\n\n\n# TODO - Call the daily_reminder() function\n\n",
